S.FORM: Don Asmonga nalecuhan i American, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. 2 bulad 15 demiad, 1928 a mihca, Don Asmonga, miunduay. (mapatay i 2014 a mihca) namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
